The paper focuses on Robotic Mobile Fulfillment Systems, which are primarily related to robotics (cs.RO). The use of mobile robots and pods also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the mechanisms for active pod repositioning, which involves control systems (cs.SY) and optimization algorithms (cs.MA).
